<p>2.
Christoff,
K., Irving, Z. C., Fox, K. C., Spreng, R. N., &amp; Andrews-Hanna, J. R.
(2016). Mind-wandering as spontaneous thought: a dynamic framework. Nat Rev
Neurosci, 17(11), 718-731. doi:10.1038/nrn.2016.113</p>
<p>3.
