Z, Liu X, et al. StatSnowball: a statistical approach to extracting entity
relationships[C]//Proceedings of the 18th international conference on World
wide web. ACM, 2009: 101-110.</p>
<p>[2]
<a href=\"http://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.luis.ai/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Language Understanding Intelligent Service<i class=\"icon-external\"></i></a></p>
